answers.answer: How annoying!!!!! Walk, sex, bounce on a ball, stairs, squats. All that restart my contractions. I've been on and all like that too. I'm 36 weeks today. I'm just like, let's get this show on the road!

question: 36 wks today. Saw my ob. I'm 4cm, 80%effaced and -1 station!!! He's 7.5 lbs already due to gestational diabetes n I feel HUGE! All night long had contractions 5-8 minutes apart and they stopped at 10:30 am!! Ugh...just come out already little boy!!
title: any day now!!
